    "longBusinessSummary": "SJ Group Joint Stock Company engages in the investment, development, and trading in real estate properties in Vietnam. The company offers real estate services; and rendering services for housing, urban areas, and industrial park services. It also provides management and investment consulting; sports, entertainment, and recreational services of sports facilities, amusement parks, and theme parks; advertising and real estate management; and project design consulting, project appraisal consulting, report preparation consulting, construction supervision consulting, and project management consulting services. In addition, the company engages in the preparation, appraisal, and implementation of construction investment projects; production of building materials from bricks, sand, cement, and gypsum; wholesale and retail of autoclaved aerated concrete bricks, building materials, and interior equipment; and wholesale of machines, equipment, and machine parts. The company was formerly known as Song Da Urban & Industrial Zone Investment and Development Joint Stock Company and changed its name to SJ Group Joint Stock Company in April 2024. SJ Group Joint Stock Company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
